description:
This is a 12 minute workout called '10 MIN CARDIO WORKOUT AT HOME (No Jumping/Apartment Friendly, No Equipment)' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: A 10 min, super sweaty, no jumping, full body cardio workout you can do at home or in the gym! No equipment needed! This is an apartment friendly workout so you won't disturb your neighbours! #fitness  #homeworkout  #cardio
